high_descs: turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn left to face the fridge
grab the cup out of the fridge
turn left and walk to the end of the room, then hang a left and walk until you reach the stove on your right
place the cup in the microwave above the stove, microwave the cup, then take it back out
move left until you reach the end of the room where the three brown shelves are at the end of the kitchen counter space, and turn to face the shelves
place the cup on top of the highest brown shelf in front of you
anns.task_desc: place a cup you got out of the fridge on top of the brown shelves

high_descs: Go left and stand in front of the fridge.
Take the white cup out of the fridge.
Go left, and then left again to stand in front of the stove.
Put the cup in the microwave above the stove, turn it on, and then take the cup out and shut the door.
Go to the brown shelves to the left of the counter.
Put the cup in the center of the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, then turn left again at the fridge.
Take the mug from in the fridge.
Turn left, then go straight, then turn left, then turn right to go toward the oven.
Heat the mug in the microwave above the oven.
Turn around, move forward, then turn right, then move forward, then turn right to face the shelf.
Place the mug on the center of the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the shelf.
